慢、外摆经营缺少管理实施细则、户外展示设施管理规则不明确、举办活动管理不规范等问题，完善户外广告设施管理配套制度，制定实施商圈外摆经营管理规则，优先出台位于重点商圈的规划，及时公开户外广告设施、牌匾标识设置方案。 同时，在重点商圈组织开展外摆试点，由区政府统筹组织相关部门划定外摆位，明确外摆时间、经营品类等细则，由经营者向所在街道进行网上报备，由街道对细则落实情况进行监管。出台户外展示设施设置标准规范及管理细则，明确办理流程、申请材料、办理时限等内容并向社会公布。优化促销「无需许可活动报告」内部管理流程，属地公安、消防等部门提前开展安全指导。北京日报"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-072ac04979bb4ab5c4b4b1ee7cda4350_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/581339099"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IhdahgdfL88YcEAMaCDkxNDY4MTI5IMux3p4GMAI4NkAocgk1ODEzMzkwOTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1675145446.0441098", "card_id": "Q_580924720", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 46}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "当一个人想赚钱，他会做出哪些改变？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/580924720"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IhdahgdfL88YcEAMaCDkxMzc2MjE5IJfJ0p4GMAE4T0Apcgk1ODA5MjQ3MjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "42_1675145446.0445063", "card_id": "Q_579001981", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 60}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在你看来，2022 苦吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "每个人的 2022 大致相同，又各有不同，那么你呢？觉得苦吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9d4124156e79797421fa23ecd1fe6ff1_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type"